Port the legacy threading manual tests tests/threads.cc, tests/threads2.cc, tests/threads3.cc, and tests/threads4.cc into CTest-backed tests under testsuite/ctest. Preserve the libcwd threading behavior being exercised: thread-specific debug object/channel state, thread-safe ostream locking, per-thread margins/output, pthread key/destructor interactions, and stress-style producer/consumer behavior, while replacing nondeterministic manual output inspection with robust automated checks.
